3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-x_jmofswAbqFZjgEGPaP_g">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hy-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-mriY_zga4scEJQWPV40NeQ">Vương Hy Hiền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/Tri%E1%BB%87u-V%C3%B5-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF/poem-_T90-a_5WLi8KUfDXDlq2w">Triệu Võ Đế - 趙武帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C3%82n/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-th%C3%A2n-c%E1%BB%91/poem-Ynu9lITGyvlz6AoDfCix4g">Trường An thân cố - 長安親故</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C3%82n/author-p2FSS_aHoApfOIrlh-6pOg">Lư Ân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C3%A3n-t%C3%ACnh/poem-qe07GsLG6hP6DdKIAjqODw">Vãn tình - 晚晴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
